title: How new homeowners redid their S.F. home (Hint: She’s a decorator)
text:
Photo: Liz Hafalia, The Chronicle Interior designer Jennifer Jones’ living room of her S.F. home. Interior designer Jennifer Jones’ living room of her S.F. home.
San Francisco real estate lore could be its own literary genre. There are tales of lackadaisical house hunters stumbling upon the perfect property with an unbelievably approachable price tag and stories of cash-flush billionaires dropping shocking amounts on crumbling shacks.
